{"tid":1329100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"721到底終點係邊","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T06:44:34.000Z","uid":79314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f7635579d28b38ef4291d408467dc1b5dc41d5ee","tid":1329100,"uid":79314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"金鐘？中環？西環？定點？<br />\n<br />\n事關見到有人嗌金鐘 有人嗌中聯辦<br />\n唔想到時分左人流<br />\n<br />\n金鐘可以去邊？<br />\n冇左鐵緊圍欄 多左監控<br />\n中聯辦又地勢難圍<br />\n同埋要熟下地形<br />\n<br />\n我唔用upvote downvote投票啦<br />\n同時大家睇留言個陣 記住睇埋是咪三毛<br />\n唔好俾人帶風向<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n去邊都好 都要齊裝備以不變應萬變<br />\n得返3日 唔該大家走出連登落力宣傳<br />\n大家721見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7348e1e139155a7a8b7b5011dc1414ae00203471","tid":1329100,"uid":182406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hG1AjBF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhG1AjBF.png&h=1640723c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jv4NU90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjv4NU90.png&h=a7ab1d47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gy7vSWG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgy7vSWG.png&h=ed3c7278&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oj64Xom.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foj64Xom.png&h=c796adb8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f4VYhom.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff4VYhom.png&h=414d5c36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s0cDhon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs0cDhon.png&h=0482ab9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HEQpXon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHEQpXon.png&h=4fe50969&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KeuqGP2.png